00:17.160 --> 00:18.320
Too bad Mom's not here.

00:18.400 --> 00:19.920
Don't mention her at dinner.

00:20.000 --> 00:22.680
You've been locked up here for weeks.

00:22.760 --> 00:24.240
You can't spy on them forever.

00:24.320 --> 00:25.400
I'm watching them live.

00:25.480 --> 00:27.280
<i>We go to the same school.</i>

00:27.360 --> 00:30.120
Renan's in prep school
and he's writing a novel.

00:31.520 --> 00:33.080
<i>A letter, for you.</i>

00:33.160 --> 00:34.640
That's Elvira's handwriting.

00:34.720 --> 00:37.280
"I'd like for us
to spend Christmas together."

00:37.360 --> 00:38.400
"A fresh start."

00:38.480 --> 00:39.760
I can't.

00:42.000 --> 00:43.520
<i>Aren't you glad to see me?</i>

00:43.600 --> 00:45.360
Sure. Are you eating with us tonight?

00:46.040 --> 00:47.160
Will your mom be there?

00:47.760 --> 00:48.800
<i>-No.</i>
<i>-Where is she?</i>

00:48.880 --> 00:49.960
<i>No idea.</i>

00:51.040 --> 00:53.240
I need money. Hire me back.

00:53.320 --> 00:54.960
You were fired for misconduct.

00:55.560 --> 00:56.840
<i>Hi, Isa.</i>

00:56.920 --> 00:58.280
I have nowhere to sleep.

00:58.360 --> 00:59.360
I can help out.

01:00.520 --> 01:02.560
-I have a sofa bed.
-Mr. Brunet?

01:06.120 --> 01:08.640
A NETFLIX ORIGINAL SERIES

01:29.200 --> 01:30.880
-Good morning.
-Morning.

01:37.640 --> 01:38.600
Some tea?

01:42.920 --> 01:43.760
