17:15.440 --> 17:17.720
My dad taught me how to develop pictures.

17:19.120 --> 17:20.040
The old way.

17:29.360 --> 17:30.200
What's up?

17:32.680 --> 17:33.520
Nothing.

17:40.960 --> 17:41.920
You're being weird.

17:45.080 --> 17:46.400
