17:55.160 --> 17:56.000
Got it.

17:57.880 --> 18:00.000
-We have to go anyway.
-Right.

18:01.240 --> 18:03.880
-My mock <i>bac</i> is today.
-Let's go.

18:44.600 --> 18:48.360
<i>This is Patrick, leave a message.</i>

18:48.440 --> 18:50.600
Hi Patrick, it's Sandrine.

18:50.680 --> 18:52.480
Leaving you one more voicemail.

18:52.560 --> 18:54.000
I guess you're busy.

18:54.560 --> 18:56.880
Call me. Bye.

19:12.000 --> 19:12.840
Who is it?

19:13.440 --> 19:15.880
Sandrine. I can't handle her.

19:15.960 --> 19:17.320
Do you have the fidelity card?

19:17.400 --> 19:20.640
The specials only apply
to clients who take the card.

19:23.120 --> 19:25.760
Try "Elvira Giannini."

19:27.400 --> 19:29.440
Your wife's card?

19:30.680 --> 19:33.880
Ex-wife, actually. Does it still work?

19:34.600 --> 19:37.400
